body:
Hey, I'm alexanderjoe10 from cryptoDevelop and we are accepting requests for projects.
We currently do Windows, Android, Linux/Ubuntu, and make Websites! We have very good projects and we work for free... So if you would like a project go to our Request A Project Area on our website @ www.cryptodevelop.net.

Please make requests as detailed as possible, otherwise it will be ignored.



Thanks,
~cryptoDevelop
